{"tid":237840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】警方：除民陣外，暫無其他團體在七一book場","createTime":"2017-05-10T15:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T16:19:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56c6b6623cdc64ee006daeebfa62d33d23be5fb5","tid":237840,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1329702-20170510.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1329702-20170510.htm&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=29fda148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1329702-20170510.htm&h=2bfb42cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1329702-20170510.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣表示，接獲康文署口頭通知，根據「性質優先」內部指引，今年七一不批准他們租用維園足球場作遊行起點，場地將租予「香港各界慶典委員會」辦慶回歸活動。民陣說，未知使用維園草地的申請會否同樣被拒。由2003年以來，民陣七一遊行也在維園起步。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆本台查詢時表示，除了民陣外，暫時無接獲其他團體在七一的時候，在維園舉行公眾活動，亦無收到民陣通知會更改起步點。康文署暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n香港各界慶典委員會名譽會長譚耀宗表示，當局將場地租予慶委會合理，因為慶委會有廣泛代表性，政府正推動慶回歸20周年，活動值得支持。他其他團體可於其他地方舉辦活動，不一定要在維園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1ead640d0daf2057bc4a6ed83c98aff8ddae08","tid":237840,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"驚犬養唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df478b9c3689ab3a2de015e93f3b4dd766cb8da","tid":237840,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"照響維園 搞寸埋佢個party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3cb24db8fe32bff659d18f28937df6f1ae9c86","tid":237840,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚犬養唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維園做唔到起點，差